---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - FishLog" description="FishLog Privacy Policy. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your data.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">Last Updated: January 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">FishLog collects the following types of information:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Email, name, and profile data when you create an account</li>
          <li><strong>Catch Data:</strong> Photos, species, measurements, locations, and conditions you log</li>
          <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, OS version, and app settings</li>
          <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> GPS coordinates when you enable location services</li>
          <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with the app to improve our services</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">We use your information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Provide and improve our fishing log and AI identification services</li>
          <li>Sync your data across devices</li>
          <li>Generate personalized analytics and insights</li>
          <li>Send you updates and fishing tips (with your consent)</li>
          <li>Ensure app security and prevent abuse</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Your data is stored securely using industry-standard encryption. Catch photos and data are stored locally on your device and, if you enable sync, in Apple's iCloud or our secure cloud servers. We never sell your personal data to third parties.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Export your data at any time</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your account and data</li>
          <li>Opt out of marketing communications</li>
          <li>Control location and photo permissions</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">5. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We use third-party services for authentication (Apple Sign In, Google Sign In), weather data, and analytics. Each service has its own privacy policy governing their use of your data.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">6. Contact Us</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          For privacy-related questions or to exercise your rights, contact us at:
          <a href="mailto:privacy@fishlog.app" class="text-ocean-blue hover:underline">privacy@fishlog.app</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
